name: BrainFeeder Fragment 1.75 [Machinery]
description:
The machine was silent, submerged in the deep methane lakes on what we used to call Earth.
A terminal in standby, untouched for thousands of years. 
[Activate] 20.000.000 nanomachine cubes emerging, assembling, and creating fluid structures.
This, was one of the first experiments of AI nanorobots, dating back to the inception of DAT network.
By RubenFro - Twitter: @Ruben_Fro
